title: Piers Morgan storms off set after confrontation over his attacks on royal couple
author: Washington Post
description:
Commentators and politicians in Britain and the United States on March 8 said the revelations in Harry and Meghan’s  interview with Oprah Winfrey were a “bombshell” and “shocking.” Read more: https://wapo.st/30ufZfk. Subscribe to The Washington Post on YouTube: https://wapo.st/2QOdcqK
